Cross dresser Idris Okuneye popularly known as Bobrisky has taken to his social media page to issue a warning to Dubai-based Nigerian big boy, Mompha.  Recall that after fulfilling bail condition yesterday. Speaking in an Instagram post, Bobrisky warned him to be careful because some fake people are already saying they are happy about his release. Mompha“Mompha welcome home. Now you have to know d people who truly love you. I’m already seeing some snitch Bastard message, saying…they are happy. I fear human being,” Bobrisky wrote. Source